capabilities.description:
Search for Rocket.Chat channels by name or topic.

Use this to find specific channels when you know part of the name.

Examples:
- Find project channels: { "query": "project" }
- Find channels by topic: { "query": "support" }

List Rocket.Chat users with pagination.

Returns user list with basic information for each user.
Use rocketchat_lookup_user for detailed information about a specific user.

Examples:
- List users: {}
- Paginate: { "limit": 20, "offset": 40 }
